1. バックグラウンドスペクトル(水,石英)の除去¶

  1. 測定した水のスペクトルに対して，僅かに含まれる石英を除去
  2. 測定した石英のスペクトルに対して，僅かに含まれる水を除去
  3. 測定したサンプルから1,2で得られたスペクトルを除去

「除去」をsubtract_background()として実装

def background_subtract(
        data             :pd.Series, 
        background       :pd.Series, 
        bg_range         :tuple,
        acceptable_slope :float      =1e-5,
        show_process     :bool       =True
    ):
    """
        dataから定数(k)倍したbackgroundを差し引く
        その際,bg_range区間を一次の近似(y=ax+b)した際の近似直線の傾き(a)が最小となるようにする

        Parameters
        ----------
        data       : バックグラウンドを含むスペクトル
        background : dataから取り除きたいバックグラウンドスペクトル
        bg_range   : バックグラウンドスペクトルを含む区間の開始indexと終了index 右端を含まないので注意:(]
        acceptable_slope :　1次近似曲線の傾きの次数
    """
    data        = pd.DataFrame({"raw":data})
    ramanshift  = pd.Series(data.index)
    background  = pd.Series(signal.savgol_filter(background, 31, 2),index=ramanshift)
    ramanshift_bg_range = ramanshift.iloc[bg_range[0]:bg_range[-1]]
    
    #print(ramanshift_bg_range)
    
    figsize = (15,6)
    if(show_process):
        fig = plt.figure(figsize = figsize)
        plt.plot(data      ,label="Target Spectrum")
        plt.plot(background,label="Subtractive Background")
        plt.axvspan(ramanshift_bg_range.iloc[0],ramanshift_bg_range.iloc[-1],color="gray", alpha=0.2,label="Background region")
        plt.legend()
        plt.show()

    preb_k = 0
    #指定した領域で， y = ax + b として近似
    #aが小さくなる abs(preb_a)>preb(next_a) ようにバックグラウンドの係数(k)を更新
    preb_a,preb_b = np.polyfit(ramanshift_bg_range, data.loc[ramanshift_bg_range, "raw"], 1)
    next_k = acceptable_slope*100
    data.loc[:, "current_estimete"] = data.loc[:, "raw"] - next_k*background
    next_a,next_b = np.polyfit(ramanshift_bg_range, data.loc[ramanshift_bg_range, "current_estimete"], 1)
    
    
    fig, ax = plt.subplots(figsize = figsize)
    ax.plot(ramanshift, data.loc[:, "raw"], label=f"Init bg_coef:{preb_k:.5f}")
    
    loop_counter = 0
    
    #更新で傾きが小さくなるようにwhileで繰り返す
    if (abs(preb_a) > abs(next_a)):
        if preb_a > 0:
            while next_a > 0:
                loop_counter +=1
                preb_k = next_k
                preb_a = next_a
                next_k += acceptable_slope*100
                data.loc[:, "current_estimete"] = data.loc[:, "raw"] - next_k*background
                next_a,next_b = np.polyfit(ramanshift_bg_range, data.loc[ramanshift_bg_range, "current_estimete"], 1)
                if(loop_counter%20==0):
                    ax.plot(ramanshift, data.loc[:, "current_estimete"], label=f"bg_coef:{preb_k:.5f}")
                
            next_k = preb_k
            data.loc[:, "current_estimete"] = data.loc[:, "raw"] - next_k*background
            next_a,next_b = np.polyfit(ramanshift_bg_range, data.loc[ramanshift_bg_range, "current_estimete"], 1)
            while preb_a > 0:
                loop_counter +=1
                preb_k = next_k
                preb_a = next_a
                next_k += acceptable_slope
                data.loc[:, "current_estimete"] = data.loc[:, "raw"] - next_k*background
                next_a , next_b = np.polyfit(ramanshift_bg_range, data.loc[ramanshift_bg_range, "current_estimete"], 1)
                if(loop_counter%20==0):
                    ax.plot(ramanshift, data.loc[:, "current_estimete"], label=f"bg_coef:{preb_k:.5f}")
        
        else:
            while preb_a < 0:
                loop_counter +=1
                preb_k = next_k
                preb_a = next_a
                next_k += acceptable_slope*100
                data.loc[:, "current_estimete"] = data.loc[:, "raw"] - next_k*background
                next_a,next_b = np.polyfit(ramanshift_bg_range, data.loc[ramanshift_bg_range, "current_estimete"], 1)
                if(loop_counter%20==0):
                    ax.plot(ramanshift, data.loc[:, "current_estimete"], label=f"bg_coef:{preb_k:.5f}")
                
            next_k = preb_k
            data.loc[:, "current_estimete"] = data.loc[:, "raw"] - next_k*background
            next_a,next_b = np.polyfit(ramanshift_bg_range, data.loc[ramanshift_bg_range, "current_estimete"], 1)
            while preb_a < 0:
                loop_counter +=1
                preb_k = next_k
                preb_a = next_a
                next_k += acceptable_slope
                data.loc[:, "current_estimete"] = data.loc[:, "raw"] - next_k*background
                naet_a,next_b = np.polyfit(ramanshift_bg_range, data.loc[ramanshift_bg_range, "current_estimete"], 1)
                if(loop_counter%20==0):
                    ax.plot(ramanshift, data.loc[:, "current_estimete"], label=f"bg_coef:{preb_k:.5f}")


    final_k = preb_k if abs(preb_a) <= abs(next_a) else next_k
    final_a = preb_a if abs(preb_a) <= abs(next_a) else next_a
    data.loc[:, "final_estimete"] = data.loc[:, "raw"] - final_k*background

    ax.plot(ramanshift, data.loc[:, "final_estimete"], label=f"Final bg_coef:{preb_k:.5f}")
    ax.axvspan(ramanshift_bg_range.iloc[0],ramanshift_bg_range.iloc[-1], color="gray", alpha=0.2,label="background region")
    ax.set_title(f"Final bg_coef:{final_k:.5f} loop_counter:{loop_counter} slope:{final_a:.8f}")
    plt.xlabel("Ramanshift[${cm}^{-1}$]")
    plt.ylabel("Intensity[a.u]")
    plt.legend()
    if(show_process):
        plt.show()
    plt.close()

    return data.loc[:, "final_estimete"]

#純粋なバックグラウンドを得る
#模擬データのバックグラウンドは正規分布のため，regionを適切に設定すると(正規分布の平均がreginoの中心に来るように設定)と不具合が生じる
#実データで同様の不具合が生じるか検討の余地あり
# water_region  = (1800 ,2000)
# quartz_region = ( 100 , 180)

#NOTE 実用上は下記のようにピークの裾-ピーク頂点(裾から裾までの区間で最大強度を持つ箇所)までの区間としたほうが良い結果を得られる
#しかし，結局ピークでは無い方の端の選択が出来ないのがネック
water_region  = (1600 ,2000)
quartz_region = ( 100 , 300)
water_peakindex  = background_df.reset_index().iloc[water_region[0]:water_region[-1],:]["water"].idxmax()
quartz_peakindex = background_df.reset_index().iloc[quartz_region[0]:quartz_region[-1],:]["quartz"].idxmax()
water_region  = (water_peakindex ,            2000)
quartz_region = (            100 ,quartz_peakindex)

pure_quartz = background_subtract(background_df["quartz"],background_df["water" ],water_region ,0.00001,show_process=True)
pure_water  = background_subtract(background_df["water"] ,background_df["quartz"],quartz_region,0.00001,show_process=True)

fig = plt.figure(figsize=(12,8))
ramanshift = spectra_df.index
bg_subtracted_df = pd.DataFrame(index=spectra_df.index,columns=spectra_df.columns)
for i,cell_name in enumerate(spectra_df.columns):
    print(f"Subtract :{cell_name}")
    spectrum =  background_subtract(spectra_df[cell_name],pure_water ,water_region  ,0.0001,show_process=False)
    spectrum =  background_subtract(spectrum             ,pure_quartz,quartz_region ,0.0001,show_process=False)
    bg_subtracted_df[cell_name] = spectrum
    ax = fig.add_subplot(2,2,i+1)
    ax.plot(spectra_df[cell_name],label="Before")
    ax.plot(spectrum             ,label="After")
    ax.axvspan(ramanshift[water_region[0] ],ramanshift[water_region [-1]-2], color="gray", alpha=0.2,label="Water region")
    ax.axvspan(ramanshift[quartz_region[0]],ramanshift[quartz_region[-1]-2], color="gray", alpha=0.2,label="Quartz region")
    ax.set_title(cell_name)
    ax.legend()
plt.tight_layout()
plt.show()
